  <brief_title>NIRF Trial: Near-Infrared Spectroscopy for Intraoperative Restriction of Fluids Trial</brief_title>
  <acronym>NIRF</acronym>
  <official_title>Near-Infrared Spectroscopy for Intraoperative Restriction of Fluids Trial A Prospective Randomized Study of Near-infrared Spectroscopy Directed Fluid Therapy vs Standard Fluid Therapy in Patients Undergoing Open Elective Colorectal Surgery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
